cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language parsing. It could also belong to "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) and "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as it uses a bi-LSTM scoring system and transition-based parsing, which are common techniques in these fields. Additionally, it could belong to "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks, and "cs.DS" (Data Structures and Algorithms) as it deals with parsing structures.
